<P><HI>Mr. BECKWITH's Di&s;cour&s;e On 2 King. 4.26.</HI></P>
<Q><P>Run now, I pray thee, to meet her, and &s;ay unto her, Is it well with thee? Is it well with thy Husband? Is it well with the Child? And &s;he an&s;wered, It is well.</P></Q>
